{"about_the_game":"Battle demons and undead attorneys, and win souls to pay back your student loans! At the elite demonic-law firm of Varkath Nebuchadnezzar Stone, you'll depose a fallen god, find romance, and maybe even make partner, if you don't lose your own soul first. <br><br>&quot;Choice of the Deathless&quot; is a necromantic legal thriller by Max Gladstone, Campbell Award-nominated author of Three Parts Dead and Two Serpents Rise. The game is entirely text-based--without graphics or sound effects--and fueled by the vast, unstoppable power of your imagination. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore a fantasy realm with a rich and evolving backstory, based on the novels published by Tor Books. <br></li><li> Play as male or female, gay or straight, dead or alive (or both). <br></li><li> Build your career on carefully reasoned contracts, or party all night with the skeletal partners at your firm. <br></li><li> Navigate intrigue and mystery in a world of scheming magicians and devious monsters. <br></li><li> Look for love in at least some of the right places. <br></li><li> Balance student loans, sleep, daily commute, rent payments, and demonic litigation\u2014hey, nobody said being a wizard was always fun.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Aid a Goddess","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/318310/c8314cab49c8f40874a684b9a1f454f481e80add.jpg"},{"name":"Become a Partner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/318310/c8314cab49c8f40874a684b9a1f454f481e80add.jpg"},{"name":"Become a Skeleton","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/318310/772c49c897ee3879f76815a81e28f2b2ae734414.jpg"},{"name":"Bright College Years","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/318310/46a1c9266def2a9a87d4f76651c2303764fce528.jpg"},{"name":"Brutal Politician","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/